&lt;li&gt;Build clean, reusable, and maintainable abstractions that will be used by Airtableâ€™s engineers for years to come.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take full ownership of components of Airtableâ€™s infrastructure, including responsibility for reliability, performance, efficiency, and observability of our production environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
